		<title>Free Privacy Policy and Terms of Service Builder</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/webhostingshow/~3/qYQpUNG8tdg/</link>
		<comments>http://www.webhostingshow.com/2012/06/04/free-privacy-policy-and-terms-of-service-builder/#comments</comments>
