		<item>
		<title>Domain and Keyword Stats Checker</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/webhostingshow/~3/ZNkqJx7D_xM/</link>
		<comments>http://www.webhostingshow.com/2012/05/02/domain-and-keyword-stats-checker/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 02 May 2012 12:48:37 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>mitch@mitchkeeler.com (Mitch Keeler)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Beginner Help]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[domain]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[keywords]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[seo]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[stats]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[tools]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[web-hosting]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[web-hosts]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[webstatsdomain]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.webhostingshow.com/?p=4007</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[When in any business, even web hosting, you want to keep an eye on your competitor&#8217;s website. You need to be able to analyze and understand the keywords they are popular for and find out the reasons why.&#160; One tool that helps you track down statistical information on keywords and domains is WebStatsDomain.&#160; The great [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="Domain and Keyword Stats Tool" border="0" alt="WebStatsDomain Review" src="http://www.webhostingshow.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/web-stats-domain.png" width="240" height="36"></p>
<p>When in any business, even web hosting, you want to keep an eye on your competitor&#8217;s website. You need to be able to analyze and understand the keywords they are popular for and find out the reasons why.&nbsp; One tool that helps you track down statistical information on keywords and domains is <strong>WebStatsDomain</strong>.&nbsp; </p>
<p><span id="more-4007"></span>
<p>The great thing that makes this website service really work is they collect detailed information about keywords and how they effect search engine results.&nbsp; It also notes the&nbsp; keywords and plenty of other statistics from your potential rivals and similar sites so you can see where you are going right or wrong and enables you to react.&nbsp; </p>
<p>To use it, simply type in a keyword you have in mind – and click search.&nbsp; To get a pretty good profile of a website (your own or somebody else’s) simply type in the domain name and click search.&nbsp; Some of the information is off (This website is worth well over $3,000) but for the most part they do a good job at giving you organic keywords, similar sites, summary statistics, and other public information about a website in one simple location.</p>
<p>Want to give it a shot? Head on over to <a href="http://www.webstatsdomain.com/" target="_blank">webstatsdomain.com</a> to get started.&nbsp; </p>
